{
  "id": "adv_card_ai_05_01",
  "title": "小美山愛 1話 一人だけゼロ回",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、今回の沖縄合宿は\n本っっっ当っっにお手数をおかけします！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ I apologize for causing\nso much trouble with this Okinawa training camp!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.8324490547
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "このご恩は、小美山愛、一生を懸けて\n必ずお返しいたしますから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll definitely repay this favor‚\nAi Komiyama‚ with all my heart!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.7700779756,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.2338093758
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "そんなにかしこまらなくていいよ\n俺のことは気にせず合宿に集中してくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You don't need to be so formal.\nJust focus on the training camp‚ don't worry about me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.8072126042,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "こころから聞いていると思うけど\n俺は、莉央さんと葵に内緒でこっそりついて行くよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sure Kokoro told you‚\nbut I'll secretly follow without Rio-san and Aoi knowing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.3881580604,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.1338093758
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "これまた本当に申し訳ありません……\n{user}さんのこと、邪魔者みたいに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm really sorry about that too…\nFeeling like I'm intruding on {user}-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.555219836,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "私はもちろん、こころだって\n本心ではそんな風には思ってないんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ that's not how I truly feel‚\nneither for Kokoro.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.6900524958,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.6442851068
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "新曲作りはもちろんだけど\n莉央さん達と夏を楽しむのも、合宿の目的なんだろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know the main purpose of the camp is to work on the new song‚\nbut also to have fun with Rio-san and Aoi during summer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.7425490063,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "俺がついて行くと\nどうしても仕事中心っぽくなるしな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I'm around‚\nit will inevitably become work-centered.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "そう言っていただけると、少し気が楽になります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So hearing that from you puts my mind at ease.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "でも、何かトラブルがあったら表に出て行くからな\nアイドルを守るのが俺の仕事だから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But if any trouble arises‚ I'll step forward to handle it.\nIt's my job to protect the idols.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "はい、それはもう！　かえって心強いです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ that's so reassuring!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "本当は、女の子だけで遠くに行くの、ちょっぴり怖くて\nもし、変な人達にからまれたらどうしよう、とか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Honestly‚ going far away with just girls makes me a little scared.\nWhat if we get involved with weird people…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "拉致されて、どこか遠くの国に売り飛ばされたら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "or get abducted and sold to some foreign country…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それは心配性過ぎるんじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "T-That's being overly anxious‚ isn't it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "……はっ！　すみません！\nそれ、たまに先輩達にも言われます……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ah! I'm sorry!\nSenpais tell me that sometimes too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "沖縄で困ったことがあったら\nこっそり相談しに来てくれ。フォローするから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If something troublesome happens in Okinawa‚\ncome and talk to me secretly. I'll back you up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます！\nやっぱり{user}さんは頼りになります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you so much!\nI can always rely on you‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんも、私達のことは\nほどほどでいいですから、沖縄を楽しんで下さいね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ please enjoy Okinawa\nwithout worrying too much about us!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――沖縄",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Okinawa",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.1
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（内緒で見守るとは言ったけど、冷静に考えると）\n（物陰に隠れて、女の子を見守ってるこの状態って……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I said I'd secretly watch over them‚ but when I think about it calmly…）\n（Hiding in the shadows and watching over the girls…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（……俺、ストーカーみたいじゃないか？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I kinda look like a stalker‚ don't I?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-coast-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 121.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01-ai012.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、お疲れ様です\n喉、乾いてませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ hello!\nIs your throat dry?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01-ai013.m4a",
      "text": "スポーツドリンクを買って来ました！　はい、どうぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I bought a sports drink! Here‚ take it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう。でも、俺のことはあまり気にしないでくれ\n莉央さんも葵も勘が鋭いから、見つかっちゃうかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks‚ but don't worry too much about me.\nRio-san and Aoi have keen instincts; they might find out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01-ai014.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　……でも、{user}さんは\nこんなに暑いのにスーツなんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes!… But‚ {user}-san‚\neven though it's so hot‚ you're still in a suit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、俺にとっては仕事だし……変かな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I am working… Is it weird?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
